== English ==
=== Spelling variants ===
* [[practice]] ([[American English]])

=== Noun ===
In [[Commonwealth English]], '''practise''' is never used as a noun.  The form used is '''[[practice]]''', the same as in American English.

=== Verb ===
This spelling is only used in [[Commonwealth English]].

# To repeat an activity as a way of improving one's skill.
# To perform or observe in a habitual fashion, as in the 'practising one's religion'.
# To pursue a career.  (Most commonly refers to [[law]] or [[medicine]]).
# To [[conspire]].  (Archaic).

